There is traditional local costume for dressing up, arts and crafts, mini tennis courts, stargazing telescopes, and a special children’s pool.

During the day you lunch next to the main pool. In the evening, you can choose from a traditional Moroccan restaurant offering mouth-watering local cuisine, or you can opt for the main restaurant which offers a mixture of cuisines.

